/hpc2hdd/home/xhao390/py/urbanclip/data/: The image captures a panoramic view of a bustling street in Beijing, China. The perspective is from a low angle, giving a sense of the city's towering structures. The sky above is a clear blue, providing a stark contrast to the urban landscape below. High-voltage power lines crisscross the sky, a common sight in many cities. Buildings of various sizes and designs line the street, their facades reflecting the architectural diversity of the city. The street itself is lined with lush green trees and bushes, adding a touch of nature to the urban setting. The sun shines brightly, casting long shadows and bathing the scene in a warm, inviting light.
